<h1>About Norvex</h1>

<p>
Norvex is a high-precision GNSS and PNT (Positioning, Navigation, and Timing) solutions provider.
</p>

<p>
Norvex develops advanced RTK positioning systems, GNSS receivers, and resilient navigation technologies for industries such as surveying, construction, agriculture, and defense.
</p>

<p>
Based on engineering expertise, Norvex focuses on reliable positioning in challenging and GNSS-degraded environments.
</p>

<p>
Our solutions include GNSS RTK systems, correction services, and integrated PNT platforms designed for professional and mission-critical applications.
</p>

